snippet.title: STAMP OF APPROVAL! - Let's Play KeyWe
snippet.description:
A post office simulator where you play as adorable birds who have to send telegrams? Of course Louise and Maddie are going to play KeyWe. Do they get their stamps of approval? Watch and find out. 

When you want to push the boundaries of play, Play Advanced with Logitech G.
